headline: Oracle (NYSE:ORCL) Expands Cloud Collaboration With Red Hat For AI-Powered Solutions
summary: Oracle (NYSE:ORCL) has been making significant strides with its recent partnership with Red Hat, focusing on enhancing hybrid cloud capabilities and AI integration. This expanded collaboration, coupled with validations for Oracle software on Red Hat OpenShift, exemplifies Oracle's commitment to advancing its cloud services. headline: VA looks to increase Oracle EHR deployments
summary: Secretary Doug Collins told lawmakers last week that the agency is hoping to roll out the software to 20 to 25 sites in fiscal year 2027, after largely halting new deployments in 2023.
